description._content:
Catalog #: 15_001655
Title: Hawker Sea Fury FB Mk 11 
Date: August 31, 1998
Creation Place: Elvington Air Show, Yorkshire, England.
ADDITIONAL INFORMATION: Originally delivered to the Royal Australian Navy in 1952, it eventually went to Lloyd A. Hamilton, Santa Rosa, CA. Then to the U.K. and Paul J. Morgan of Sywell. Flown as ""Baby Gorilla"". Overturned during landing, Sywell, UK, May 12, 2001. Morgan fatally injured in the accident. Presently being restored in Sweden.
